caller_intent: William wanted to discuss his auto policy renewal with National General and update his credit card information, as well as schedule an in-person meeting to address his new car.
resolution_steps: Bina reminded William about his expiring credit card linked to his National General auto policy.
Bina requested William to notify them if he obtains a new credit card for updates.
William agreed to schedule an in-person meeting on Wednesday or Thursday.
Bina confirmed the meeting and offered assistance with the policy renewal.
summary: Bina from Alliance Insurance contacted William to inform him about his expiring credit card on his National General auto policy and scheduled an in-person meeting to discuss the renewal and his new car. William agreed to the meeting and confirmed he would bring his new car details for discussion.
